OL,3,C'My mum took her own life, I want the
OL,4,Cright to choose when to die'
OL,6,FA man who has the same incurable
OL,7,Fillness which drove his mother to take
OL,8,Fher own life is calling for people
OL,9,Fwith similar conditions to be given
OL,10,Fthe "agency" to decide when to die.
OL,12,FJosh Cook's mother, Lisa, decided to
OL,13,Fend her life at 57 rather than face
OL,14,Fthe prospect of a slow, painful death
OL,15,Fcaused by Huntington's disease.
