OL,3,C'My mum took her own life, I want the
OL,4,Cright to choose when to die'
OL,6,FThe 33-year-old former semi-
OL,7,Fprofessional rugby player, from
OL,8,FHuddersfield, inherited the same
OL,9,Fneurodegenerative condition and knows
OL,10,Fthat he is likely to endure a gradual
OL,11,Fdecline in health that will result in
OL,12,Fhis death.
OL,14,FMr Cook is supporting a bill brought
OL,15,Fforward by the Spen Valley MP Kim
OL,16,FLeadbeater that would legalise
OL,17,Fassisted dying.
OL,19,FHis mother had campaigned for a law
OL,20,Fchange for more than a decade before
OL,21,Fher death.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
