OL,3,C'My mum took her own life, I want the
OL,4,Cright to choose when to die'
OL,6,FMr Cook said: "I have a very long,
OL,7,Fslow decline in my future to an
OL,8,Feventual end of choking to death on my
OL,9,Fown saliva or not knowing who my loved
OL,10,Fones are.
OL,12,F"Kim's bill offers the hope for
OL,13,Fsomeone like me to take agency and
OL,14,Fcontrol at a point in my life where I
OL,15,Fwon't have any."
OL,17,FMr Cook had been out playing rugby
OL,18,Fwhen he returned to the home he shared
OL,19,Fwith his mother to find she had taken
OL,20,Fher life in June this year.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
