OL,3,C'My mum took her own life, I want the
OL,4,Cright to choose when to die'
OL,6,FHe believes she had not told anyone of
OL,7,Fher plans because she feared he might
OL,8,Fface prosecution. Helping someone to
OL,9,Fend their life can carry a maximum
OL,10,Fprison sentence of 14 years.
OL,12,FMr Cook said: "She had to do this by
OL,13,Fherself without support and without
OL,14,Fanyone to say goodbye."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
