OL,3,C'My mum took her own life, I want the
OL,4,Cright to choose when to die'
OL,6,FMs Leadbeater's bill, which faces a
OL,7,FCommons vote on Friday, would allow
OL,8,Fadults who have mental capacity, are
OL,9,Fterminally ill and in the final six
OL,10,Fmonths of their life to request
OL,11,Fassistance from a doctor to end their
OL,12,Flife.
OL,14,FShe said: "There are far too many
OL,15,Ffamilies that I have met that have
OL,16,Fexperience of harrowing deaths, often
OL,17,Fwhere people have very good palliative
OL,18,Fcare, but it's not not able to meet
OL,19,Ftheir needs.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
