OL,3,C'My mum took her own life, I want the
OL,4,Cright to choose when to die'
OL,6,F"It has left them with deep trauma and
OL,7,Ftheir families with deep trauma."
OL,9,FMPs rejected a similar bill in 2015
OL,10,Fand the latest proposals have proved
OL,11,Fdeeply divisive, with both the justice
OL,12,Fsecretary and health secretary among
OL,13,Fthose to publicly question them.
OL,15,FITV News has approached all MPs about
OL,16,Ftheir voting plans ahead of Friday's
OL,17,Fdebate.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
