OL,3,C'My mum took her own life, I want the
OL,4,Cright to choose when to die'
OL,6,FIn the Calendar region, of those who
OL,7,Fresponded, 19 said they would vote in
OL,8,Ffavour of the bill, 11 intend to vote
OL,9,Fagainst, 18 said they were undecided
OL,10,Fand one said they would abstain from
OL,11,Fvoting.
OL,13,FBoth Mr Cook and his mother were part
OL,14,Fof campaign group Dignity in Dying,
OL,15,Fwhich supports assisted dying for
OL,16,Fthose whose suffering is unbearable.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
