OL,3,C'My mum took her own life, I want the
OL,4,Cright to choose when to die'
OL,6,FThey argue that, along with good care,
OL,7,Fdying people who are terminally ill
OL,8,Fand mentally competent adults deserve
OL,9,Fthe choice to control the timing and
OL,10,Fmanner of their death.
OL,12,FHowever, the campaign group Assist us
OL,13,Fto Live believes the government should
OL,14,Fprioritise reforming social care and
OL,15,Fpalliative care.
OL,17,FRachael Tomlinson, who has multiple
OL,18,Fsclerosis, said: "Social care is on
OL,19,Fit's knees, we want social care to be
OL,20,Fimproved and for and disabled people
OL,21,Fto receive appropriate support."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
