OL,3,C'My mum took her own life, I want the
OL,4,Cright to choose when to die'
OL,6,FProf Allan House, a former director of
OL,7,Fthe Leeds Institute of Health
OL,8,FSciences, believes there needs to be
OL,9,Ffurther reassurances about how
OL,10,Fvulnerable people are protected.
OL,12,FHe added: "I would want to do much
OL,13,Fmuch more than just decide if they
OL,14,Fhave mental capacity."
